[source] DROP TABLE

exec source
CREATE TABLE whitebear(id INT PRIMARY KEY, t TEXT default 'In the vast and desolate expanse of the northern mountains, where snow-capped peaks pierced the sky and icy winds howled relentlessly, there resided Snowy, a small white bear with a peculiar aversion to showering. Despite the frigid surroundings, Snowy found every excuse to avoid the soapy water, much to the chagrin of his patient mother. She tried every trick in the book to coax him into cleanliness, from promises of delicious honey treats to playful games, but Snowy remained steadfast in his resistance. Yet, fate had a peculiar way of intervening in Snowy s life one crisp morning. As he ventured through the dense woods surrounding their mountainous home, curiosity led him to a clearing where a glistening blue lake lay hidden amidst the trees. Drawn by its shimmering allure, Snowy approached cautiously, his nose twitching with intrigue. However, fate had other plans, and with an unexpected slip, Snowy found himself plummeting into the icy waters below. Panic seized him as the cold shock enveloped his body, but amidst the chaos, a surprising revelation dawned upon him: he could swim! With newfound confidence, Snowy paddled through the crystalline depths, the water cleansing away his fears and uncertainties. Emerging from the lake, Snowy returned home with a newfound zest for cleanliness, regaling his mother with tales of his unexpected adventure and proving that sometimes, the greatest discoveries lie in the most unexpected of places. In the vast and desolate expanse of the northern mountains, where snow-capped peaks pierced the sky and icy winds howled In the vast and desolate expanse of the northern mountains, where snow-capped peaks pierced the sky and icy winds howled In the vast and desolate expanse of the northern mountains, where snow-capped peaks pierced the sky and icy winds howled In the vast and desolate expanse of the northern mountains, where snow-capped peaks pierced the sky and icy winds howled In the vast and desolate expanse of the northern mountains, where snow-capped peaks pierced the sky and icy winds howled')
----
[source] CREATE TABLE

